---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Main from "../components/Main.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Mobile Tyre Service in Nottingham & Newark | Tyre Emergency Ltd"
    description="Tyre Emergency: Fast, reliable mobile tyre fitting and repair services in Nottingham & Newark. Available 7 days a week with a 60-minute response time. Call now for immediate assistance with your tyre emergency."
>
    <Hero
        heading="Mobile Tyre Service in Nottingham & Newark"
        tagline="We Come to You at Home or Roadside Today"
        bgImg="url(/img/mobile-tyre-fitting.jpeg)"
        btnText="Call Now"
    />
    <Main
        h1="Tyre Emergency"
        h2="Rapid Mobile Tyre Services in Nottingham & Newark"
    >
        <p class="lead">
            In need of a quick tyre fix in Nottingham or Newark? Look no
            further. At
            <strong class="fw-bold">Tyre Emergency</strong>, we pride ourselves
            on providing prompt and reliable emergency tyre fitting services,
            right at your doorstep or by the roadside. Whether it's a flat tyre
            or a routine replacement, our team is equipped to handle it all with
            efficiency and care.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
            Our expert mobile tyre fitters are on call <strong
                >seven days a week</strong
            >, ready to serve you across the wide expanse of <strong
                class="fw-bold">Nottingham and Newark</strong
            >. We understand the inconvenience of tyre troubles, which is why we
            aim to reach you within <strong>60 minutes</strong> of your call,
            ensuring minimal disruption to your day.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
            From standard cars to light commercial vehicles, we have the
            expertise and equipment to service a variety of vehicle types.
            Safety, convenience, and promptness are at the heart of what we do,
            making us your go-to solution for all tyre emergencies.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
            <strong>Need urgent tyre assistance?</strong> Don't hesitate to
            contact us. Our team is ready to swiftly respond to your needs and
            get you back on the road safely and quickly.
        </p>
    </Main>
    <CTA />
</Layout>
